				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You'll want to use Ward of Xegony exclusively. Not only does it tank significantly better than the Epic pet, but you'll be able to take down higher level monsters with ease, whereas the Epic pet will get slaughtered. From a cleric's perspective, its a huge difference.
<br />

<br />
Not only that, but Epic pet cannot land procs on monsters higher than level 62.
<br />

<br />
Water pet 51+ is NOT a tank. Don't use it as such.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=204546" target="_blank" class="postlink">Arch Mage Xalmat Lunaire</a>
