				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Once you reach 61, you'll only use your epic pet in a specific fight config : 
<br />
- Your opponents cannot be 61+
<br />
- Your pet is not tanking but only meant to do DPS.
<br />

<br />
That's right, it's the usual config of LDON normal (level 65 dungeons), and personnally it's the only place where I still use my epic pet and damn, it rocks.
<br />

<br />
While having fun in sebilis or howling stones it might be cool also, but remember, not as a tank.<br />_________________<br />Thaumaturge <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=381021" target="_blank" class="postlink">Majax Seplu`Komavan</a>
